* About 20 minutes walk from {{ill|lt=Tokai Railway Company|Q513679|WD=Q513679|lt=JR|1=Central Japan Railway Company}}{{ill|lt=Tokaido Line (Nagoya area)|Q11235139|WD=Q11235139|lt=Tokaido Main Line|1=Tōkaidō Line (JR Central)}} {{ill|lt=Odaka Station|Q871424|WD=Q871424|1=Ōdaka Station}}.

